Mapazi e[[Hugabe]] (Responsible Authorities) - pakushanda kunoita hushangazhi pane mapazi ehurumende akapiwa [[hugabe]] (authority) kuti ave anotarira kuti mitemo yakasiyana yehurumende yatevedzwa.  Mapazi e'''hugabe''' aya anobata basa zvichienderana nemitemo yakatarwa nedare reParamende - (Acts of Parliament). MuZimbabwe kune Mapazi e'''hugabe''' anoti: Zimra; Zimre; Zinwa; Zinara; Municipalities; Natural Resources Board; Environmental Protection Authority zvichingodaro.  '''Hugabe''', izwi rinotodza shoko rokuti '''ubugabe'' rinobva kumutauro wekunyika yeBurundi unonzi Kirundi, richireva '''authority'''.
